The paper discusses a visual analytics system for exploring and selecting machine learning models, which involves human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The focus is on generating accurate predictive models, which falls under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of holdout data for verifying model performance, which is a common practice in information retrieval (cs.IR) and database systems (cs.DB).
